e,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n26971"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A7%D9%90%D9%86%D9%92%D8%B7%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%82%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be free, to be loose"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to go ahead, to set out, to proceed, to go off"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/in.tˤa.la.qa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26971","headword_ar":"انطلق","root":"Tlq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AinoTilaAqN","text_ar":"اِنْطِلَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which the dim. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuTayoliyqN","text_ar":"نُطَيْلِيقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", the conjunctive"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"being rejected, so that it becomes"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"niTolaAqN","text_ar":"نِطْلَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, loosed from his bond:"},{"kind":"text","text":"whence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AinoTilaAqu AlEinaAni","text_ar":"اِنْطِلَاقُ العِنَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The rein's being let loose,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slackened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is a phrase metonymically used to denote quickness in going along. (Har pp. 355-6.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a captive loosed from his bond)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went his way:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or [simply]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he went away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"departed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he went removing from his place."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA.) Thus in the Kur [lxxvii. 29],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AinoTaliquwA A_ilY maA kunotumo bihi tuka*~ibuwna","text_ar":"اِنْطَلِقُوا اـِلى مَا كُنْتُمْ بِهِ تُكَذِّبُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Depart ye to that in which ye disbelieved"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (TA;) meaning to the punishment: (Bd, Jel:) or, accord. to IAth, [it seems to mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"go ye away quickly"},{"kind":"text","text":"into the lowest depth of misery or affliction; for he says, app. in explanation of this verse of the Kur, that]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAinoTilaAqu","text_ar":"الاِنْطِلَاقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suroEapu","text_ar":"سُرْعَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al*~ahaAbi fiY A^aSoli AlmiHonapi","text_ar":"الذَّهَابِ فِى اَصْلِ المِحْنَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And one says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AnTlq yafoEalu ka*aA","text_ar":"انطلق يَفْعَلُ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went away doing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to do, such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA@noTalaqa A@lomalaA^u minohumo","text_ar":"وَا@نْطَلَقَ ا@لْمَلَاُ مِنْهُمْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ani A@mo$uwA","text_ar":"اَنِ ا@مْشُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the Kur xxxviii. 5 may be expl. in a similar manner;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^an","text_ar":"اَن"},{"kind":"text","text":"being here used in the place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaquwluwna","text_ar":"يَقُولُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or this] means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And the chief persons of them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"broke forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"launched forth, with their tongues,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"saying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Go ye on,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"continue ye, in your course of action"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (Mughnee, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano","text_ar":"اَنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AunoTuliqa bihi","text_ar":"اُنْطُلِقَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, was taken away;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) like as one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AunoquTiEa bihi","text_ar":"اُنْقُطِعَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O.) ―         -b3-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AnTlq lisaAnuhu","text_ar":"انطلق لِسَانُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His tongue was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, free from impediment;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eloquent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chaste in speech."},{"kind":"text","text":"See an ex. in the Kur xxvi. 12: and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taluqa lisaAnuhu","text_ar":"طَلُقَ لِسَانُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AnTlq","text_ar":"انطلق"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of the face: see 1, latter half, in two places."}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","Mgh","K","Bd","Jel"]}]}}